data.description: 2 BEAUTIFUL ACRES AND A GORGEOUS MOVE IN READY 4 BEDROOM PLUS DEN , 2 BATH JACOBSEN CONSTRUCTED TRIPLE WIDE MODULAR HOME. FEATURES A SPACIOUS LIVING AREA AND KITCHEN WITH GE APPLIANCES. LARGE LAUNDRY ROOM AND PANTRY. WALK-IN CLOSET IN THE EXPANSIVE MASTER SUITE. SLIDING GLASS DOORS OPEN FROM DINING AREA TO REAR OF HOUSE. HUGE DOUBLE SHED/WORKSHOP (BOTH SIDE SWITH ELECTRIC, ONE WITH A/C) WITH A LARGE COVERED CARPORT. RV HOOK UPS WITH 30 AMP, 110 ELECTRICAL AND DUMP STATION IN PLACE AND READY TO USE . FLOORING COMPLETELY REPLACED WITH VINYL PLANKING. OFF THE BEATEN PATH PROVIDES PLENTY OF PRIVACY. A MUST SEE FOR YOU AND YOUR FAMILY!!   ONE YEAR HOME WARRANTY IS INCLUDED.
